{"tid":806950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(直播)琴日俾傳銷拎完錢，叫緊佢還","createTime":"2018-09-05T06:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T12:24:14.000Z","uid":84217,"like":4,"dislike":105,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"9d687c7a5cdcf7b9bdc69a592258ca2032f1415b","tid":806950,"uid":84217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:44:40.000Z","msg":"首先大家可以話我on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我絕對明白<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 真係咪撚同d仆街做朋友<br />\n<br />\n琴日上到去已經心都寒撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你當人朋友人地當你on9<br />\n到兩個人帶我去禁錢<br />\n再不斷聽班人同你講自己心路歷程<br />\n一路其實都幾灰<br />\n已經諗唔到野<br />\n<br />\n可能你話點解唔走，乜乜乜<br />\n其實成個場咁多人睇住你，真係走唔到<br />\n可能你話點解要俾錢<br />\n因為我有，而我冇諗過會去果度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返到去諗過少少錢就咁算，<br />\n但真係愈諗愈嬲<br />\n就同佢講其實我唔係on9叫佢搞好退款書俾我<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/143850_50b862eb3c75b41882fdba46408e6a7a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F143850_50b862eb3c75b41882fdba46408e6a7a.png&h=f3fc3162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢暫時剩係咁答我<br />\n我話冇可能，叫佢搞好俾我<br />\n<br />\n已上網揾好記者<br />\n呢兩日冇起色就會用其他手段"},{"pid":"81a5ca8025d322a7f1c8dce9ccdb83e7471602cc","tid":806950,"uid":84217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0e20bf89715218042637c17e99623a2de3cfdf","tid":806950,"uid":83340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:47:08.000Z","msg":"岩啦，呢d朋友唔搵人搞佢已經好比面"},{"pid":"43060d752f8dc5eddcf8ffff14415efd042ca21a","tid":806950,"uid":68098,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:47:22.000Z","msg":"on lun 99 <br />\n行咪行囉<br />\n洗唔洗擇日呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e92bdb0e08b4ec5025b